    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/e4b421fa289c27150912511760147ed0.webp?t=1732666238\" width=601 height=23 /></span><br>Hello! Welcome to the 'about this game' section for The Dreamer Must Die. Don't forget to SMASH that Wishlist button and give a Follow. I hope you really enjoy this game description dude, it's So Awesome!! You can trust me, I'm a cute lil' smiley guy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/f737e71a2cd7b44c47fbce4d66e8a694.avif?t=1732666238\" width=601 height=136 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/dc146a49c75f872a4d3e980ee74fe4e6.poster.avif?t=1732666238\" width=601 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/dc146a49c75f872a4d3e980ee74fe4e6.webm?t=1732666238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>A mysterious figure named The Dreamer has appeared in the dream world, and summoned an ominous tower that looms over the sky. If that's not bad enough, shadowy creatures have begun to spawn and is causing all forms of torment on the residents. However, they do have one last hope left, you. <i>But is hope really enough?</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/436ff498a80780586418dfd0e5f07dbd.poster.avif?t=1732666238\" width=601 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/436ff498a80780586418dfd0e5f07dbd.webm?t=1732666238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The dream has become a dangerous nightmare, infested with shadow-spawn that appear in many varieties. Utilize a wide range of equipment, level your character, upgrade your arms, to make the most of you are given. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/34f50a8d44a6cd68d5da4cb64b559ffb.poster.avif?t=1732666238\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/34f50a8d44a6cd68d5da4cb64b559ffb.webm?t=1732666238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/c7d09eb18a0d215afe805e8c49c04654.poster.avif?t=1732666238\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/c7d09eb18a0d215afe805e8c49c04654.webm?t=1732666238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/a1d3d0d73531760fc3764588fd4d5b2f.poster.avif?t=1732666238\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/a1d3d0d73531760fc3764588fd4d5b2f.webm?t=1732666238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/87a29a4c798ee80d684918a8116b9265.apng?t=1732666238\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/87a29a4c798ee80d684918a8116b9265.poster.avif?t=1732666238\" class=\"bb_img\" width=601 height=150 /></picture></span><br>Ahlquist Interactive is a startup development studio. A.I. hell-bent on the goal of creating fun and unique games that leave a lasting impression. Currently on this project there's Hunter Ahlquist for programming, art assets, and direction, and John Della Franco for music.<br>Be sure to join the A.I. Discord server and drop a hello!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/e4b421fa289c27150912511760147ed0.webp?t=1732666238\" width=601 height=23 /></span><br>WOW, you really read all of that! I'll be honest, that description reads like every other description on this platform, I'm surprised that your eyes didn't roll to the back of your head. And I mean who even is this &quot;Hunter Ahlquist&quot; guy anyway? He introduced himself like some kind of household name... Regardless, I <i>hope</i> you're interested in the game, Hunter wont feed me until I hit my wishlist quota.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116590/extras/aa6b048d77805512077554d20c2ce4cb.avif?t=1732666238\" width=601 height=136 /></span>",
